================================================================

FastZip is a compressor/decompressor just for FastQ/FastA files.

================================================================

1. Condition

	1-1. Hardware
		16GB RAM at least

	1-2. Software
		Linux OS
		GCC 3.4.x above

================================================================

2. Installation

	2-1. Download
		https://github.com/CorgiWang/FastZip_v1

	2-2. Generate Executable File
		$ make
		$ sudo cp ./fastzip /usr 

	2-3. Set Environmental Variables
		......		

================================================================

3. Usage

	3-1. Compression
		fastzip -E Input Output

	3-2. Decompression
		fastzip -D Input Output

================================================================
